(23, 'ACT012', 'Bali Junggle Swing', 'air', '1;', '6619434e977b1_Pasted image 37.png;6619434e9b31e_Pasted image 38.png;', '<p>We devised the Bali Swing Tour for those of you who want to enjoy swings on the island of Bali with the very beautiful terrain in the forest. It is an adventurous activity that is genuinely unlike any other. Despite the fact that swinging is a relatively new activity in Bali, both local and foreign tourists enjoy swing activities due to their passion. If you want a stunning backdrop but are terrified of heights and don&rsquo;t want to risk Swing, you can perch on a massive bird&rsquo;s nest suspended between two trees. The service provider will offer a ladder for you to access and exit the building.</p>', 'bali-jungle-swing-bali', 'en', '2024-04-12 14:21:10', '2024-04-12 14:21:10'),
