(41, 'DST021', 'Geger Beach', 'south', '661a7675c22aa_Pasted image 69.png;661a7675c4a26_Pasted image 70.png;', '<p>Geger Bali beach is not well known among Indonesian tourists on holiday in Bali. However, if you&rsquo;ve been to The Mulia resort in Nusa Dua or The ST Regis Bali, you&rsquo;ve been to Geger beach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tourists are better familiar with the names Geger and Nusa Dua Bali beach. The majority of the Geger beach area is available to the public, with the northern section of the beach seeing the most visitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>North Beach</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the northern part of Bali&rsquo;s Geger beach you will find lots of chairs for sunbathing, and rental of water sports equipment. Such as snorkeling equipment, scuba diving and surf boards. Most tourists who do not stay at one of the resorts on Geger beach will go to the northern part of Bali&rsquo;s Geger beach area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to use the sundeck for sunbathing or you want to sit in the shade, then you have to pay for the sundeck rental.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>South Beach</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you walk from the north side of the beach to the south side of Geger beach, then you will find two very beautiful luxury resorts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Namely The St. Regis Bali Resort and The Mulia Resort. Because of the cleanliness and beauty of Geger beach, it combines with the beauty of the ITDC area and on the beach there are luxury resorts. So Geger beach Nusa Dua got the nickname The Hidden Paradise Of Bali.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The southern coastal area is quieter and there are sundek with umbrellas. Sundecks and umbrellas, provided by the resort, for guests staying overnight. Hotel guests usually order drinks at the resort area bar which is in the beach area. In addition, near the Bar area there is also a swimming pool for resort guests.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most of the Geger Nusa Dua beach area is managed by the hotel. Because it is managed by a hotel, Geger Bali beach is very clean, and every day there will be cleaners who always clean this beach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Beach Attraction</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The attractiveness of Geger Beach Nusa Dua lies in the beauty of the white sand beach, with a fine sand texture. The contours of the beach are sloping, with a one-kilometer stretch of beach. What I like most about Geger beach Nusa Dua is the cleanliness of the beach which is always maintained.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The waves on this beach are very calm and very shallow. This makes Geger beach Nusa Dua in favor of tourists who vacation in Bali with children, and tourists who are on their honeymoon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Geger Beach Entrance Ticket Prices</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every beach visitor who does not stay at one of the resorts in the Geger beach area of Bali, will be charged an entrance fee. Then how much is the entrance ticket to Geger beach Nusa Dua? The following is a table of ticket prices for Geger beach Nusa Dua Bali.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ticket Price Category</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Entrance ticket price IDR 5,000/person.</li>\r\n	<li>Car Parking IDR 5,000 / Car.</li>\r\n	<li>Motorbike Parking IDR 2,000 / motorbike.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Location of Geger Beach Nusa Dua</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The location of Geger Bali beach is a little hidden and far from the center of the crowd. Because the location of Geger beach is hidden, many Indonesian tourists choose other beach attractions in Bali as holiday destinations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But for those of you who want to find a quiet white sand beach atmosphere, safe for children to swim. Then Geger Bali beach is the most suitable beach location for you to visit, besides Jimbaran Bali beach.</p>', 'geger-beach-nusa-dua', 'en', '2024-04-13 12:11:39', '2024-04-13 12:11:39'),
