(69, 'DST035', 'Nung Nung Waterfall', 'north', '661b1c3f3c334_Pasted image 99.png;661b1c3f4018e_Pasted image 100.png;', '<p>The Nungnung Waterfall is located in Pelaga Village, Petang, Badung, Bali. The waterfall attraction is located in a highland area surrounded by pure water and dense, green trees, providing a gorgeous and spectacular backdrop. This tourist site is popular with both foreign and domestic visitors due to its gorgeous surroundings and pure water, as well as its easy position. Nungnung waterfall was once a relatively infrequently visited tourist destination due to the difficulty of accessing the location cupuk. Following the construction of access to the spot and several support poles, the nungnung waterfall tourist attraction became popular and frequently visited by tourists.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nungnung Waterfall Location</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The location of the Nungnung Waterfall is located in Pelaga Evening Village, Badung Bali. If you drive from Kuta or Denpasar, it will take about 60 minutes to travel and armed with a google map, you will have no trouble finding the location of this Nung Nung waterfall, because it is located on the main road to the evening village. If you don&rsquo;t want to bother driving alone, here we from Bali Tour offer Bali Car Charter transportation services at low prices and very satisfying service, accompanied by a friendly, patient and experienced driver will make the trip to the location of the nungnung waterfall very enjoyable. . The tourist destination of the Nungnung Waterfall has always been a charm in the hearts of tourists, with the beauty and beauty of this waterfall, it always makes tourists want to linger in this very beautiful location of Nung Nung Waterfall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nungnung Waterfall History</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Previously before 1996 this place was only a natural dish where there were inaccessible shrubs and the surrounding scenery that could not be enjoyed up close. Along with the development of tourism on the island of Bali, making this place is used as a tourist attraction, the construction of access roads to the location, so that many tourists flock here to enjoy the magnificence of this very beautiful natural work. For those of you who are bored with the bustling city atmosphere with pollution and congestion, then visiting the nungnung waterfall tourist attraction can be a solution to break the deadlock in your head by enjoying the beautiful water that falls from a height with views of green plants around cliffs and clear water, the very fresh air will make your body and mind refreshed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Height of Nungnung Waterfall</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The exhausting trek to the place will be worth it for the spectacular natural scenery. The cliffs, which are covered with green tropical flora and have crystal pouring water, will enhance your natural tourism. The Nung Nung waterfall, with roughly 50 meters in height, is quite tall in comparison to other waterfalls. This height will enhance the splendor of this waterfall excursion. Making the air fresh enough at an altitude of 900 feet below sea level will help your blood circulation. If you enjoy waterfalls, we recommend paying a visit to the Nungnung waterfall tourist attraction. This waterfall is in high demand among tourists because, in addition to its impressive height, the water outpouring is impressive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Facilities at Nungnung Waterfall</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The facilities at Nungnung Waterfall are quite complete and adequate, there is a large parking area, so you don&rsquo;t have to worry about finding a parking space for your vehicle. The road to the waterfall from the parking lot is quite good, just a long walk to reach the location, because it is located far in the middle of the forest, on the way there is access to stairs which are very helpful and there is a resting place in the middle of the trip, if you feel tired, you can rest in this gazebo while enjoying the scenery around which is so enchanting. There is a toilet located in the parking lot, you can use this toilet if needed. There is also a small shop selling food and drinks here, if you feel thirsty, you can buy it here. We think this facility is so complete and you don&rsquo;t need to hesitate anymore if you go to the nungnung waterfall whose charm is always memorable on tourists hearth</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'nung-nung-waterfall-bali', 'en', '2024-04-13 23:58:58', '2024-04-13 23:58:58'),
