(85, 'DST043', 'Aling Aling Waterfall', 'north', '661b258806663_Pasted image 112.png;661b2587f2c8e_Pasted image 111.png;', '<p>Aling Waterfall is a tourist attraction in the Bali districts of Sambangan, Sukasada, and Buleleng. In this Bali Interest Place, we will go over the Aling &ndash; Aling waterfall in great detail. This waterfall, like many others in the highlands, is found in the highlands, where the air is quite cool, resulting in incredibly pure and rather cold water. This tourist site is certainly worth seeing if you are visiting the northern portion of Bali, which is well-known for its numerous magnificent waterfall adventures.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Beautiful Aling Aling Waterfall</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aling &ndash; Aling Waterfall is very beautiful, it&rsquo;s no wonder that many foreign and domestic tourists flock here to appreciate the exotic natural works and this place is also used as a photo object uploaded on Instagram. The water discharge in Aling &ndash; Aling waterfall is very heavy, causing the sound of gurgling water that seems to call you to enjoy the work of nature, with green plants around the waterfall making a very fantastic view that seems to make you feel life in nature and will build your soul your nature lover. With fantastic natural beauty it will make you feel at home for a long time in this waterfall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A very popular waterfall tourist attraction in the northern area of the island of Bali, if by chance you are passing by this place, we recommend paying attention to the Aling &ndash; Aling waterfall, to see the beauty of this waterfall, by going through the paths around which are still natural. many green trees feel like in a forest, very suitable for those of you who like trekking and nature tourism. When you get close to the location, you can hear the sound of water falling from a height which will add a very beautiful impression</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Height Aling Aling Waterfall</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your efforts in going through the path wi