rea which is quite large, there are small stalls and shops selling snacks and mineral water, and along the route to the waterfall, there are many art shops selling souvenirs and handicrafts, and you can stop for a moment here if you want to buy souvenirs. your family or friends. It&rsquo;s not far from the waterfall place, there is a place for taking a rest while enjoying the beautiful panorama of rice terraces and Buleleng Beach. In order to visit the Gitgit waterfall, all visitors will follow the walkway down until the spot point. This road is one of the omissions in the Dutch era where the local residents use it to access other regions. In 1975, this waterfall was opened as a tourist destination in the northern part of Bali. Since it is designated as a tourist destination in Bali, many tourists from domestic and foreign countries visit this waterfall and is one of the famous tours in Bali to visit this place</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What You Can Do at Gitgit Waterfall</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a very famous tourist destination in the northern area of the island of Bali, where the Git git waterfall has a very beautiful charm, it is not inferior to other waterfall tourist destinations, with the natural scenery around which is still natural, it will make the atmosphere of visiting this git git waterfall. be very comfortable, the gust of wind that brings the waterfall splash on your face will feel very cool. Enjoy a very natural forest atmosphere with clean water from unpolluted mountain springs. A very valuable moment to enjoy the beauty of nature&rsquo;s fantastic work, the sound of falling water will accompany you in exploring the beauty of the Git Git waterfall, there are several things you can do here</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Splashing Water</strong>: Enjoying the beauty of this very beautiful gitgit waterfall, with clear and cold water that will pierce the pores and make your body fresh, a very rare sensation in spending time with the splash of the very famous gitgit waterfall in the northern area of the island of Bali. So don&rsquo;t miss this rare opportunity to enjoy the fresh water at this git git waterfall</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Nature View</strong>: Around the waterfall there are natural views that are no less beautiful, with the green color around which is still very natural, it will create an atmosphere like in the forest with the sound of a very beautiful waterfall, enjoy the natural surroundings that are still very natural with very clear water once will create a real atmosphere like in the forest</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Photography</strong>: If you really like photos, then this place is perfect for you, with a high waterfall and greenery around it will make the photos very pictursque and very instagramable, so it&rsquo;s not wrong if you visit the Gitgit waterfall which is in this git git village, is Rare experience for take picture with the famous waterfall and most beautiful waterfall in this area</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Pathway to Gitgit Waterfall</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The location of the waterfall is a bit far from the parking area, you will walk down the pathway for about 30 minutes to arrive at the location, along the way the scene changes and on both sides you can see coffee and clove trees. It is a refreshing experience to walk in this quiet area where the birds take turns to sing. The water is cool and gradually gets colder when you approach the waterfall. A short distance from the waterfall, the fine water spray will cool your body. Sometimes the atmosphere will become misty. The journey is very tiring but when it is close to the Gitgit waterfall, the fatigue during the trip will disappear and be replaced with a sense of awe of the natural beauty that this has to offer, the sound of falling water will make you feel like you want to hurry to the location and the cool air will accompany you to enjoy the beauty of this very famous git git waterfall. We from Bali Tours provide transportation facilities for those of you who want to visit the beauty of the Git Git waterfall, while the prices we offer are relatively cheap with a private car along with a friendly and experienced driver that will make this natural waterfall tour very enjoyable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'air-terjun-git-git-bali', 'id', '2024-04-14 00:42:51', '2024-04-14 00:42:51'),
(89, 'DST045', 'Sekumpul Waterfall', 'north', '661b27199d7b6_Pasted image 116.png;661b271998492_Pasted image 115.png;', '<p>The Bali Sekumpul cascade is a tourist attraction in the Bali town of Sekumpul, Buleleng. This Bali Interest Place is particularly famous among visitors because it provides unrivalled natural beauty, with the sound of flowing water and lush trees around the cascade adding to the allure of this excursion. It is not surprising that many foreign and local travellers visit this tourist destination simply to enjoy nature&rsquo;s magnificent work. In addition to admiring its beauty, many people swim in this waterfall pool, and many people capture the experience by photographing it and sharing it to social media, where it receives a lot of likes from readers. Spending time on the island of Bali and seeing spectacular Sekumpul waterfall provides a completely unique experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>location of the Sekumpul waterfall</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The location of the Sekumpul waterfall is in the interior and far from village settlements, so it can be classified as a hidden waterfall tour because of the access that is far from the hustle and bustle of the city. It is the same with other waterfall attractions where the location is a bit deep and quiet, as well as this waterfall tour, to reach the location it takes good stamina because you will go through a long path accompanied by descending stairs, maybe to get to the location. the location of the waterfall is not that tiring, but it is different to return it will require good stamina where through the path and the stairs facing up, this will be very draining of stamina. But for those of you who have an adventurous spirit, this will not be an obstacle because the results you get are very worth it. Your fatigue will be relieved when you see the amazing work of nature where seeing a waterfall that stands majestically on a high cliff with the beautiful sound of the gurgling water will make your holiday experience in Bali feel complete</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How To Get There</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Another interesting thing about walking along the winding paths is seeing the shady and fresh trees on the left and right of the road and passing through local community plantations where there are lots of clove trees, here the tree can grow fresh because it is in a cool highland. never lacked water. Going down the stairs, with a range of about 360 steps with a distance of 300 meters with a duration of about 30 minutes, finally you can reach the location, from a distance you can see a high waterfall where 2 streams of water flow in this waterfall, the sound of gurgling water can be heard from afar which will make you even more curious to quickly approach the location of this Sekumpul waterfall. But to reach the location you have to cross a small river where the depth is only human, a challenge that must be overcome to see the beauty of the Sekumpul waterfall. After passing through a small river, you will arrive at the location of this magnificent waterfall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The uniqueness of Sekumpul Waterfall</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The uniqueness of this Sekumpul waterfall tour is from its height, which reaches about 100 meters in height, and has been named the highest waterfall on the island of Bali, besides that there are also two streams of water that fall from this waterfall, where these two streams are sourced. of two different streams of water from the plateau. This unique thing can be seen during the dry season where the two streams of water have different colors. One where one stream of water comes from a spring in the hills in the village of Sekumpul and the other one flows from the river in the village of Sekumpul. The two streams fall in a different pool below, so it can&rsquo;t be categorized as a twin waterfall, here you can choose to choose to swim in a pool with small water or heavy water. This makes it a special and unique waterfall on the island of Bali.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'sekumpul-waterfall-bali', 'en', '2024-04-14 00:45:17', '2024-04-14 00:45:17');
