(91, 'DST046', 'The Blooms Garden', 'north', '661b282ee4635_Pasted image 117.png;661b282eeaaa0_Pasted image 119.png;661b282ee7d50_Pasted image 118.png;', '<p>The Blooms Garden Bedugul is a highland tourist site that offers cool air, fresh, pure air, and a stunning view of flower gardens. A tourist attraction inspired by the beauty of Bandung&rsquo;s gardens and Dubai&rsquo;s Miracle Park. The surrounding natural beauty is breathtaking, and not just because it is teeming with gorgeous flowers and plants.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Blooms Garden Bedugul is significantly more gorgeous with a mountainous backdrop and captures the hearts of visitors. Those who are tired of the rush and bustle of city life will find the beautiful green landscape and peaceful atmosphere at this Tabanan tourist attraction pleasant and revitalising.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ticket Entrance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The entrance ticket price for The Blooms Garden Bedugul is very affordable. For local or domestic tourists, the children category will be charged a ticket of IDR 10,000. Meanwhile, adult local tourists over 10 years old will have to pay a ticket of IDR 20,000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unlike the case with tourists from abroad or foreign tours. For foreign tours, children aged 5-10 years will be charged IDR 20,000. Meanwhile, for adult foreign tours, an entrance ticket of IDR 30,000 will be charged</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Location Address and Route</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The address itself is at Br. Batusesa, Candikuning, Baturit, Tabanan Regency, Bali. The distance you need to travel to get to this place from the center of Tabanan is 46 km. Or it takes 1 hour 26 minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For those of you who want to visit this destination, it is highly recommended to use a private vehicle. Because public transportation facilities that go to Br. Batusesa is very limited.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Facility</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supporting facilities available specifically for visitors here include:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Very large parking lot<br />\r\nToilets are quite clean<br />\r\nTrash can<br />\r\nPath for pedestrians<br />\r\nFood court place<br />\r\nGazebo or seating<br />\r\nBicycle rental places, climbing equipment and others.<br />\r\nthe blooms garden inn<br />\r\nPicnic area</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Opening hours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This super cool Bali tourist park is open from 08.30 &ndash; 18.00 WITA. Remember, the implementation of these opening hours uses Central Indonesian time. So you need to estimate the hours where you are at the tourist location</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'the-blooms-garden-bali', 'en', '2024-04-14 00:49:54', '2024-04-14 00:49:54'),
